data.description: Stunning 6 bed/3.5 bath home in Woodbridge Estates!  Located on a quiet cul-de-sac in Glendale Schools, this home offers over 5000 SF, 3 living areas, granite counters, basement, and more!  On the main floor is a formal dining area, office space, living room with fireplace and built-ins, laundry room, and a kitchen and hearth room!  The kitchen features stainless appliances, an attached dining space with access to the back deck, adjacent powder room, and a hearth room with fireplace!  Upstairs, you will love the generous primary suite with dual vanities, a jetted tub w/skylight, walk- in shower, and an enormous closet with custom shelving.   3 more upstairs bedrooms share a full hall bathroom.  Downstairs, discover two more bedrooms, a full bathroom, plenty of storage, a media room, and large recreation room.  Outside, the deck overlooks trees and you will love the covered front porch. Quick access to Hwy 65.
